at innenfor EØS og som driver fondsmegling.<ul class="tocSubUl"><li>I</li><li>II</li></ul></li></ul></dd></dl></header><main class="documentBody" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1995-07-07-683" id="dokument"><h1>Forskrift om endring i forskrift om grenseoverskridende tjenesteyting av utenlandske investeringsforetak med hovedsete i annen stat innenfor EØS og som driver fondsmegling.</h1><section class="section" data-name="kapI" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/" id="kapittel-1" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1995-07-07-683/KAPITTEL_1" data-partID="k1"><h2 data-text-align="center">I</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1">I forskrift av 27. september 1994 nr. 905 om grenseoverskridende tjenesteyting av utenlandske investeringsforetak med hovedsete i annen stat innenfor EØS og som driver fondsmegling gjøres følgende endringer:</article> <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">§ 1 første ledd punkt 2 skal lyde:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="2)" data-name="2)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">2)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">som ønsker å drive fondsmegling i Norge gjennom grenseoverskridende virksomhet.</article></article></li></ul></article> <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">§ 2 nytt siste punkt skal lyde:</article><article class="defaultP">Kvalifisert investor: Foretak som i følge siste årsregnskap har en beskattet egenkapital på minst 10 millioner kroner.</article> <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">§ 6 nytt annet ledd skal lyde:</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2">For investeringsforetaks fondsmegling her i riket knyttet til utenlandske verdipapirer og rettet mot kvalifiserte investorer gjelder følgende bestemmelser i verdipapirhandelloven:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="a)" data-name="a)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">a)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-1-ledd-1">kap. 1 om alminnelige bestemmelser,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="b)" data-name="b)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/2/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">b)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1">kap. 2 om emisjoner,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="c)" data-name="c)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/3/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">c)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-3-ledd-1">kap. 2a om opsjoner til verdipapirer, terminer,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="d)" data-name="d)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/4/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">d)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-1">§ 29 om taushetsplikt i fondsmeglervirksomhet, og</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="e)" data-name="e)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/5/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">e)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1">§ 62 om straff.</article></article></li></ul></article> <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">§ 6 annet ledd blir nytt tredje ledd som skal lyde:</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3">Annet ledd gjelder tilsvarende for investeringsforetakets øvrige fondsmegling her i riket. I tillegg gjelder følgende bestemmelser i verdipapirhandelloven:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="a)" data-name="a)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">a)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-1-ledd-1">§ 18 om god meglerskikk,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="b)" data-name="b)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/2/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">b)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-2-ledd-1">§ 19 om opplysningsplikt,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="c)" data-name="c)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/3/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">c)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-3-ledd-1">§ 22 om ansattes verdipapirhandel,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="d)" data-name="d)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/4/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">d)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-4-ledd-1">§ 24 om fondsmegleres adgang til å drive næringsvirksomhet mv,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="e)" data-name="e)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/5/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">e)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-5-ledd-1">§ 25 om kredittgivning,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="f)" data-name="f)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/6/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-6"><span class="data-originalId">f)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/6/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-6-ledd-1">§ 26 om regnskapsplikt,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="g)" data-name="g)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/7/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-7"><span class="data-originalId">g)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/7/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-7-ledd-1">§ 27 om suspenderte verdipapirer mm,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="h)" data-name="h)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/8/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-8"><span class="data-originalId">h)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/8/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-8-ledd-1">§ 28 om kurtasje mm,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="i)" data-name="i)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/9/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-9"><span class="data-originalId">i)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/9/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-9-ledd-1">kap. 3 del III om sikkerhetsstillelse,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="j)" data-name="j)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/10/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-10"><span class="data-originalId">j)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/10/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-10-ledd-1">kap. 3 del IV om kontroll med verdipapirer,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="k)" data-name="k)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/11/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-11"><span class="data-originalId">k)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/11/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-11-ledd-1">kap. 4 om verdipapirhandel gjennom fondsmeglerforetak, og</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="l)" data-name="l)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/12/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-12"><span class="data-originalId">l)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/3/punkt/12/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-3-punkt-12-ledd-1">kap. 5 om aktiv forvaltningsservice.</article></article></li></ul></article></section><section class="section" data-name="kapII" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/" id="kapittel-2" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1995-07-07-683/KAPITTEL_2" data-partID="k2"><h2 data-text-align="center">II</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-2-ledd-1">Endringene trer i kraft straks.</article></section></main></body></html>